        "text_d94FbU": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Nina's Look 1: <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/m-l-textured-cotton-teya-highneck-top\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Monk & Lou Textured Cotton Teya Top</span></a> and <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/propaganda-tencel-linen-madison-wide-pant\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Propaganda Madison Wide Pants</span></a></p><p>Dejan’s Look 1: <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/atrium-cotton-stripe-short-sleeve-button-up-shirt\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Atrium Striped Short Sleeve Button Up Shirt</span></a>, <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/atrium-classic-cotton-jersey-crewneck-short-sleeve-tshirt-1\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Atrium Crewneck Short Sleeve T-Shirt</span></a> and <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/atrium-reverse-weave-relaxed-fleece-jogger-1\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Atrium Relaxed Fleece Jogger</span></a></p><p>Nina's Look 2: <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/propaganda-babyrib-alana-tank\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Propaganda Alana Tank</span></a> and <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/propaganda-stretch-cotton-poplin-coral-gathered-a-line-skirt\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Propaganda Coral A-Line Skirt</span></a>, </p><p>Dejan’s Look 2: <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/atrium-cotton-classic-ls-button-up-shirt\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Atrium Classic Striped Long Sleeve Button Up Shirt</span></a>, <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/atrium-classic-cotton-jersey-crewneck-short-sleeve-tshirt-1\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Atrium Crewneck Short Sleeve T-Shirt</span></a> and <a href=\"https://www.getplenty.com/products/atrium-reverse-weave-relaxed-fleece-jogger-1\"><span style=\"text-decoration:underline\">Atrium Relaxed Fleece Jogger</span></a></p>"
